high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the small dresser.
Pick the pen up from the dresser.
Turn around and go forward and then left to face the desk.
Put the pen in the cup.
Pick the cup up from the desk.
Turn around and go right to face the book shelves.
Put the cup down on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a pen on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn around, and go to the dresser behind you, with the clocks on it.
Pick up the pen on the dresser, to the left of the book.
Turn around, move forward, then turn left to go to the desk.
Put the pen in the mug on the desk.
Pick up the mug from the desk.
Turn around, go forward, then turn right to approach the shelves located to the left of the dresser.
Place the mug on the bottom left shelf
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around to locate the dresser.
Pick up the pencil from the left side of the dresser.
Carry the pencil and turn around, then turn left to locate the desk.
Place the pencil in the mug on the desk.
Pick up the mug from the desk.
Carry the mug and turn around, then right to find the bookshelf.
Place the mug and pencil on the bottom left shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug and pencil to the bookshelf.
